    <descript>
      <abstract>This point layer represents Arlington County Park's nature centers.</abstract>
      <purpose>
    The Parks geodatabase contains feature classes for all aspects of geographic
    data created by or for the Department of Parks, Recreation and Community
    Resources. The feature classes represent various types of Parks and facilities
    maintained by the County and the Northern Virginia Regional Park Authority.
